(293,'2FTISanDiego2016','Registering on the WCA website will put you on the waitling list, **you must pay before being approved**.\r\n\r\nThe cost of registration is **$7+2n** where n is the number of events you are competing in. $1 per competitor will go towards WCA and $1 will go towards SoCal cubing expenses.\r\n\r\nFor example, if you plan on competing in 3x3 and 3x3 one-handed, the cost of registration will be $7+2(2)=$11.\r\n\r\n| # of Events | Total Registration Fee |\r\n| -------- | -------- |\r\n| 1 Event    | $9     |\r\n| 2 Events   | $11     |\r\n| 3 Events    | $13     |\r\n| 4 Events    | $15     |\r\n| 5 Events    | $17     |\r\n\r\n**PAYMENTS ARE NO LONGER BEING ACCEPTED.** See you Saturday!\r\n',2,'Payments'),
