nfirmar  simples, basta apenas dar seu nome ao chegar. Algumas competies possuem taxa de inscrio e, nesses casos, veja no site se dever pagar antes ou somente no dia, no prprio local.\r\n\r\n7. Espere seu nome ser chamado\r\nTodos competiro sempre em grupos. Mesmo se vrios competidores forem chamados, e voc no, no se preocupe. Sempre ser avisado quando o ltimo grupo foi chamado. Se seu nome no for chamado aps a ltima chamada dos competidores, da procure o organizador.\r\n\r\n8. Quando chamado, traga seu quebra-cabea resolvido \r\nQuando for chamado para competir, leve seu quebra-cabea resolvido para onde indicarem. Depois se sente na rea de espera, onde deve esperar para ser chamado.\r\n\r\n9. Quando chamado, v para a mesa \r\nUma pessoa ir chamar seu nome, indicando uma mesa para voc competir, fique atento.\r\n\r\n10. Aps a resoluo, volte para a rea de espera\r\nEm uma rodada, voc ir resolver seu quebra-cabea 5 vezes (3 vezes para algumas modalidades). Depois que voc terminar uma soluo, retorne para a rea de espera e espere ser chamado novamente. Deixe seu quebra-cabea com o juiz, pois ele ser levado para ser embaralhado de novo.\r\ns vezes estipula-se um tempo de corte (veja o cronograma) para uma rodada. Voc tem 2 (ou 1 para algumas modalidades) tentativas para fazer abaixo desse tempo e assim completar as 5 resolues. Caso contrrio, far apenas 2 (ou 1). Os resultados sero listados no ranking da WCA em todo caso.\r\n\r\n11. Aps as resolues, volte para a plateia\r\nAps ter realizado as 5 resolues, voc terminou aquela rodada. Pegue seu quebra-cabea de volta e v para a plateia.\r\n\r\n12. Divirta-se\r\nNo  nenhum bicho de sete cabeas. Voc est l para se divertir, assim como todos l esto. Apenas relaxe e aproveite a competio.\r\n\r\n',4,'Meu Primeiro Campeonato'),
(7853,'1stDibrugarhOpen2018','Step 1 - Register on WCA by selecting the events you want to participate in.\r\nStep 2 - Pay the registration fee at the entrance of the college where a registration kiosk will be set up by Auxesis team.\r\n\r\nPayment fee structure:\r\n\r\nBase fee (One event) - 300 INR\r\nFor every extra event - 50 INR\r\nAnd if any of the participants is interested in buying Auxesis T-Shirt you can give your T-Shirt size in the link given below and then take it by doing payment at the registration desk.. \r\nhttps://goo.gl/forms/I2qxzOWymKnLqrfg2\r\n\r\n**EXAMPLE**\r\nSo if you are participating in 3 events, you need to pay 300(Base fee) + 100(for remaining 2 events) = 400 INR\r\n',1,'Payment'),
(7855,'1stDibrugarhOpen2018','For those of you new to cubing, WELCOME!\r\n\r\nWe wanted to let you know this event is perfectly fine for cubers of ANY age and experience. We just ask you know a couple things before coming to compete...\r\n\r\nFirst, please be familiar with the WCA Regulations, found here:\r\nhttps://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/\r\n\r\nOf course, those regulations contain a lot of legalese, so we have a video made specifically for new cubers, just to show them the basics of competing. This video will explain most of what any cuber competing for the first time will need to know.\r\n\r\nyoutube(https://www.youtube.com/embed/dPL3eV-A0ww)\r\n\r\nIf you are stoked to compete and ready to sign up, head over to the \'Registration & Payment\' tab and it will guide you to the registration.\r\n\r\n**FAQs**\r\n\r\nQ: Do I use my own cube to compete?\r\nA: YES! You are responsible for your own hardware in order to compete. This means you should bring your own cube.\r\n\r\nQ: What is the normal age of competitors at these events?\r\nA: All ages are welcome, but in general competitors are between 10 and 20 years old. Don\'t let this stop you though, everyone can and should cube!\r\n\r\nQ: How do I find results?\r\nA: All results are posted on the WCA page within a week after the competition finishes. However, for the day of competing, go to Cubecomps.com to find information about current events. This is also where you will find information about upcoming rounds of events. Remember, the results are entered by a human so please be patient if you do not see your results immediately.\r\n\r\nQ: Are there age divisions?\r\nA: Nope! All competitors compete together.\r\n\r\nQ: I want to attend, or I have friends/family who want to attend, but not compete. Do they need to pay as well?\r\nA: No. All spectators are free to view the competition at no cost. There is payment only to compete. But in some cases, venue will be having restriction to allow spectators depending on the competition.\r\n\r\nQ: Can I have fun at this event?\r\nA: HECK YES! Cubing is amazing, and we sincerely hope you enjoy the competition!\r\n\r\nIf you have any further queries, please do mail the organizers & delegates.',2,'New Competitor Information'),
(8197,'10doRioGrandedoNorte2018','![Image description](https://image.ibb.co/kZAn7q/5b375688-73f0-49ea-993b-b947d20812c4.jpg)\r\n\r\n![Image description](https://sites.google.com/site/sbcubosamostras/_/rsrc/1468739500999/config/customLogo.gif?revision=14)',3,'Patrocinadores'),
