(38430,'1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024','### SveKub\r\nDenna tvling arrangeras tillsammans med SveKub.\r\n\r\nSom medlem i SveKub har du alltid 25% rabatt p tvlingar, och medlemskapet r **gratis**!\r\nLs mer om att bli medlem [p vr hemsida](https://svekub.se/bli-medlem/) eller [bli medlem direkt](https://ebas.sverok.se/blimedlem/SveKub).\r\n\r\nFr att ta del av rabatten r det bara att vara registrerad i SveKubs medlemsregister, sedan anmler du dig som vanligt. Vi verifierar sedan vilka av de anmlda som r medlemmar och inte.\r\nDu betalar till att brja med fullt pris, men vi terbetalar 25% i samband med att anmlan granskas (godknns eller stts p vntelistan).\r\nI framtiden hoppas vi kunna ha ett ngot smidigare system, men anmlningssystemet kan i dagslget inte ha olika anmlningsavgifter fr olika personer.\r\n\r\n#### Vill du ocks arrangera en tvling?\r\n**Du kan ocks arrangera en tvling i din stad!** Det enda kravet r att du har koll p en lokal som hade passat bra fr en tvling. Det kan vara allt frn matsalar, gymnastiksalar, bygdegrdar, folkets hus och klubb- eller samlingslokaler. Sjlva tvlingen kan pg i bara ett par timmar p en vardagskvll eller en hel lnghelg, du bestmmer. Drefter kan SveKub hjlpa till med det du inte kan eller vill gra sjlv, ssom tvlingsschema, budget och hemsida. Mer information om och hur det gr till att arrangera en tvling finns [hr](https://svekub.se/arrangera/).\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### SveKub\r\nThis competition is organized together with SveKub.\r\n\r\nAs a member of SveKub, you always have a 25% discount on competitions. The membership is free, but is only available for Swedish citizens.\r\nRead more about becoming a member [on our website](https://svekub.se/en/bli-medlem/) or [become a member away](https://ebas.sverok.se/blimedlem/SveKub).\r\n\r\nTo get the discount, you simply need to be registered as a SveKub member. After that, you register as normal and we will verify which competitors are members and which are not.\r\nYou will pay the full price to begin with, but we will refund 25% when reviewing the registration (approving it or moving it to the waiting list).\r\nIn the future, we hope to have a slightly more convenient system, but the current registration system can not have different registration fees for different people.\r\n\r\n#### Do you also want to organize a competition?\r\n**You can also organize a competition in your city!** The only requirement is that you know a venue that would be suitable for a competition. It can be anything from canteens, sport halls, community centers and club or meeting rooms. You decide for how long the competition should run, anything from a couple of hours on a weekday to an entire weekend is a possibility. After that, SveKub can help with what you can\'t or don\'t want to do yourself, such as a competition schedule, budget and website. More information about and how to organize a competition is available [here](https://svekub.se/arrangera/).',1,'SveKub'),
(38431,'1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024','### Viktig info\r\n\r\n#### Frsta tvlingen?\r\n\r\nOm det hr r din frsta WCA-tvling, vlkommen! Det r viktigt att du lser igenom alla flikar hr p sidan, eftersom det finns mycket viktig information dr.\r\n\r\nOm du aldrig tvlat frut br du ha med ett giltigt ID, till exempel ett pass eller krkort, fr att intyga att dina personuppgifter stmmer. Om den tvlande inte har ett ID kan en frlder bekrfta dessa uppgifter.\r\n\r\nP [nr?] kommer vi demonstrera hur det gr till att tvla, men vi rekommenderar starkt att du ven kollar p [den hr videon](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LUU7YKnSn1g), som gr igenom hur allt fungerar p en tvling. Att lsa igenom [denna guide](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/edudoc/competitor-tutorial/se/tutorial.pdf) r ocks en bra id eftersom den visar det mesta man behver knna till som deltagare. Dessa guider fungerar som komplement till [WCA:s Regler](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/), som varje tvlande r skyldig att vara bekant med.\r\n\r\n#### Kom ihg:\r\n\r\n**Alla tvande ska ha lst [WCA:s Regler](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/).** Deltagare frvntas vara bekanta med WCA:s reglemente innan man deltar p en officiell tvling. Reglerna finns ven versatta till [svenska](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/translations/swedish/), men tnk p att det r den engelska originalversionen som gller om det skulle finnas ngra skillnader.\r\n\r\n**Du mste vara anmld till tvlingen online fr att f tvla!** Du kan anmla dig [hr](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024/register).\r\n\r\n**Du mste vara redo att tvla nr din grupp startar.** Du behver bara vara p plats i lokalen under de grenar dr du planerar att delta. Du behver dock vara p plats i lokalen senast 15 minuter innan din frsta gren ska brja, s du hinner fullflja incheckningen, och fr att vara p den skra sidan ifall schemat pverkas ngot under tvlingen.\r\n\r\n**Fotografering med blixt r frbjudet i hela lokalen!** Blixtar r strande fr tvlande. Fotografering utan blixt r tilltet.\r\n\r\n**Publik mste befinna sig 1,5 meter ifrn tvlingsstationerna och tvlingsomrdet.** Annars finns risken att man str andra tvlande eller tvlingsproceduren.\r\n\r\n**Man fr inte prata om blandningarna innan man tvlat frdigt i pgende gren.** Annars finns risken att man blir diskvalificerad.\r\n\r\n**Live-resultat finns p [WCA Live](https://live.worldcubeassociation.org/).** Dr kan du se vilka resultat du fick, och ifall du gick vidare till nsta omgng.\r\n\r\n**Du finner gruppindelningarna p [competitiongroups.com](https://www.competitiongroups.com/).** Alla tvlar inte samtidigt i de olika grenarna, utan deltagarna delas vanligtvis in i grupper. P denna sida kan du se vilken grupp du tvlar i fr de grenar du r anmld. P strre tvlingar frbestms ven exempelvis domaruppdrag fr de lite mer erfarna deltagarna, och i dessa fall finns ven dessa publicerade p hemsidan ovan.\r\n\r\n**Hll koll p er e-mail.** Ngra dagar innan tvlingen skickas ibland deltagarmail ut, dr vi tar upp diverse viktig information fr deltagare att knna till. I detta mail kommer ocks eventuella ndringar sedan tvlingen annonserades tas upp. Om det finns annan information som vi snabbt mste kommunicera till deltagare s kommer detta ocks ske via e-mail, drfr r det viktigt att ni hller koll p er e-mail regelbundet.\r\n\r\nOm du har ngra frgor, maila grna ngon av arrangrerna, vi hjlper dig grna!\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Important info\r\n\r\n#### First competition?\r\n\r\nIf this is your first WCA competition, welcome! Make sure to read through all tabs on this page as there is a lot of important information there.\r\n\r\nIf you have never competed before, you should bring a valid ID, for example a passport or driver\'s licence, to verify your birth date and nationality. If the competitor does not have an ID, a parent can confirm this information.\r\n\r\nWe will have a demonstration showing how the competing process works on [when?], but we highly recommend watching [this video](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dPL3eV-A0ww), which demonstrates how everything works at a competition. Reading through [this guide](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/edudoc/competitor-tutorial/tutorial.pdf) is also a good idea since it shows most things a competitor needs to know. These guides act as complements to the [WCA Regulations](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/), which every competitor is expected to be familiar with.\r\n\r\n#### Remember:\r\n\r\n**All competitors must have read the [WCA Regulations](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/).** Participants are expected to be familiar with the WCA Regulations before attending an official competition. \r\n\r\n**You must be registered for this competetiton online in order to compete!** You can register [here](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024/register).\r\n\r\n**You must be ready to compete when your group starts.** You only need to be present at the venue during the events in which you plan to attend. However, you need to be present at the venue no later than 15 minutes before your first event starts so that you have enough time to complete the check-in, and also compensate for any slight changes in schedule. \r\n\r\n**No flash photography in the entire venue!** Flash is distracting to the competitors. Pictures without the use of flash are allowed.\r\n\r\n**Spectators should remain 1,5 meters away from the solving stations and the competition area.** Otherwise, you might distract other competitors or disrupt the competition flow.\r\n\r\n**You are not allowed to talk about the scrambles until the round is done** Otherwise, you risk getting disqualified.\r\n\r\n**Live results can be found on [WCA Live](https://live.worldcubeassociation.org/).** There you can see what results you got, and whether you progressed to the next round.\r\n\r\n**You can find the group divisions at [competitiongroups.com](https://www.competitiongroups.com/).** Everyone will not compete in the different events at the same time, instead they are divided into groups. On this page you can see which group you compete in for the events you are registered for. At larger competitions, for example, judge assignments are also predetermined for the slightly more experienced participants, and in these cases these are also published on the website above.\r\n\r\n**Check your e-mail** A few days before the competition, you might receive a participant email where we will address various important information for participants to know. This email will also include any changes made since the competition was announced. If there is any other urgent information which we need to communicate to competitors, then it will be done through e-mail so therefore it is important that you check your e-mail regularly.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, please email one of the organizers, we will be happy to help!',2,'Viktig Info / Important Info'),
(38433,'1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024','### Resa\r\n#### Med Bil\r\nAdressen r Viksngsgatan 23, 723 47 Vsters. Det finns en parkeringsplats precis bredvid skolan. Ingng till tvlingslokalen sker frn skolgrden (mellan de tv skolbyggnaderna).\r\n\r\n#### Kollektivtrafik frn utanfr Vstmanlands ln\r\nMed bde tg och buss bokar du enklast biljett till Vsters C fr att sedan ka vidare med lokaltrafiken. Fr lokal och fjrrgende reseplanering i hela Sverige kan [Resrobot](https://resrobot.se/) anvndas. Biljettbokning fr lngdistansresor grs enklast via respektive resebolags hemsida.\r\n\r\n#### Med lokaltrafik i Vstmanlands ln (VL)\r\nFrn Vsters C gr det en buss linje 3 mot Flygplatsen via Viksng. G av vid stationen Sdergrden eller Rnnbergagatan och g en kort promenad till Viksngsskolan.\r\n\r\nAnvnd [VL](https://www.vl.se/) fr tidtabeller, biljettinformation, samt personlig reseplanering i hela Vstmanslands ln. Biljetten kper du enklast via VLs app eller genom att blippa ditt kreditkort (contactless) p bussen. \r\n\r\n--\r\n\r\n### Travel\r\n#### By car\r\nThe address is Viksngsgatan 23, 723 47 Vsters. There is a parking spot on side of the school. Enter the venue from the school yard (in between the two school buildings).\r\n\r\n#### Public transport from outside Vstmanland county\r\nWith either train or buss the destination is Vsters C and you continue the travel with local traffic. [Resrobot](https://resrobot.se/) can be used for local and long-distance travel planning throughout Sweden. Ticket booking for long-distance journeys is most easily done via the respective travel company\'s website.\r\n\r\n#### With local traffic in Stockholm County (VL)\r\nFrom Vsters C take buss line 3 towards Flygplatsen via Viksng and either get off the buss at the stop Sdergrden or Rnnbergagatan and take a short walk to Viksngsskolan. \r\n\r\nUse [VL](https://www.vl.se/) for timetables, ticket information, and personal travel planning throughout Vstmanland County. The easiest way to buy the ticket is via VL\'s app or by tapping your credit card (contactless) on the bus.',3,'Resa / Travel'),
(38436,'1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024','[![](https://cuboss.se/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/logo_400.png)](https://cuboss.se/?r=wca)\r\n\r\n### Sponsorer & Priser\r\nTvlingen sponsras av kub-butiken [Cuboss.se](https://cuboss.se/?r=wca)! Cuboss r en svensk onlinebutik specialiserad p speedcubes och andra typer av pussel, vilka de levererar bde inom Sverige samt till resten av vrlden. Cuboss har valt att sponsra tvlingen med presentkort till enligt nedan.\r\n\r\nMedaljrer i 3x3x3 tilldelas presentkort frn Cuboss enligt fljande:\r\n1:a plats: 100 kr\r\n2:a plats: 75 kr\r\n3:e plats: 50 kr\r\n\r\nDessutom kommer 1 presentkort p Cuboss vrt 100 kr att lottas ut bland deltagare p prisceremonin, dr alla som nrvarar har chans att vinna ett!\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Sponsors & Prizes\r\nThe competition is sponsored by the cube store [Cuboss.com](https://cuboss.com/?r=wca)! Cuboss is an online cube store based in Sweden, specializing in speedcubes and other types of puzzles, with worldwide delivery available. Cuboss has generously chosen to sponsor the competition with gift cards for the medalists in the various event as outlined below:\r\n\r\nMedalists in 3x3x3 will receive the following gift cards from Cuboss:\r\n1st place: 100 SEK\r\n2nd place: 75 SEK\r\n3rd place: 50 SEK\r\n\r\nIn addition, 1 gift card worth 100 SEK will be randomly drawn among competitors at the award ceremony, where everyone who attends has a chance to win one!',4,'Sponsor - Cuboss'),
