(38456,'1stBarpetaCubeOpen2024','Reach Barpeta Road Railway Station (https://maps.app.goo.gl/NGNrcxQzkeRa5FVA9). Take an Auto or E-Rickshaw available outside of Station and come to Howly Town(fare-20).Then take an E- Rickshaw from near of Howly Town Masjid (https://maps.app.goo.gl/Gzcx2WBEEHpbK6es7) \r\nand come to the Venue- Sublime Academy, Howly (fare:- 10). \r\nThe Venue is 50 meters from NH-31. \r\n\r\nIf you come via Bus or other vehicle From Guwahati by highway, The venue will be on the left of NH-31, Before reaching Howly Town. \r\n\r\nNearest major airport is Guwahati Airport (127KM via National Highway).',3,'Travel'),
(38479,'1stBarpetaCubeOpen2024','* Please check your respective mail ID\'s through which you will receive all the communications from organisation team.\r\n* All the newcomers are requested to bring their valid ID proofs with Date of Birth mentioned on it.\r\n* For the returning participants: Please claim your WCA ID if you have not claimed it yet. Link is provided below.\r\n[How To Claim your WCA ID](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3widl70-Uus)\r\n\r\n### First time participants\r\nStep 1 :- [Sign-up](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/users/sign_up) on WCA. You must mention your full name without any abbreviations while creating your WCA profile.\r\nStep 2 :- [Register](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/1stBarpetaCubeOpen2024/register) for the competition\r\nStep 3 :- Pay the correct registration fees amount according to the fees structure to this UPI ID- spondonn-1@okhdfcbank and write participant\'s name in the notes.\r\nStep 4 :- Send a screenshot of confirmation of payment to snath@worldcubeassociation.org.\r\n\r\n### Returning participants\r\nStep 1 :- [Sign-in](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/users/sign_in) using your email that you used for your previous competitions\r\nStep 2 :- [Register](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/1stBarpetaCubeOpen2024/register) for the competition.\r\nStep 3 :- Pay the correct registration fees amount according to the fees structure to this UPI ID- spondonn-1@okhdfcbank and write participant\'s name in the notes.\r\nStep 4 :- Send a screenshot of confirmation of payment to snath@worldcubeassociation.org.\r\n\r\n*Registration for the event will only be accepted if a person has registered on the WCA competition page AND made the payment.*\r\n\r\n### Fees Structure:-\r\n\r\n| Number of Events | Registration Fees |\r\n| -------- | -------- |\r\n| 1     | 300     |\r\n| 2     | 400     |\r\n| 3     | 500     |\r\n| 4     | 600     |\r\n| 5     | 700     |\r\n| 6     | 800     |\r\n| 7     | 900     |\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Notes:-**\r\n1. You can\'t change the events once the registration period closes.\r\n2. It is mandatory to **pay the registration fees** AND **register on WCA** to complete the full registration process.\r\n3. Wait for 48 hours to get your registration confirmed after payment has been done.',1,'Registration and Payment'),
