('10AniversarioGuatemala2023',0,0,'2023-09-14 20:05:31',118737,NULL,0,NULL,11000,'2023-10-13 08:41:54',1583,'10 Aniversario Guatemala 2023','Guatemala City',NULL,0,60,1,'The available space at the venue','2023-09-14 19:22:09',NULL,'[Cube Shop Guatemala](mailto:cubeshopguatemala@gmail.com)','Guatemala','2023-09-11 03:53:23','GTQ',0,'',0,'2023-10-15','2023-10-14 00:00:00',0,'',NULL,'',NULL,'Espaol\r\n\r\nInformacion de Pago:\r\nEfectuar el pago respectivo, el costo es de Q 110.00 de base que incluye participacin en cualquier categora.\r\nTambien incluye: playera, gafete y diploma de participacin. Si el pago es a partir del 30 de septiembre, ya no incluir la playera.\r\n\r\nEl pago de la inscripcin debe hacerse a la cuenta monetaria no. 3754007393 de Banrural a nombre de Adrin Ramrez. Posteriormente enviar un correo con fotografa de la boleta de pago, talla de playera (S, M, L) y su nombre (como aparece en la WCA) al correo cubeshopguatemala@gmail.com.\r\n\r\nLuego de registrarse en la pgina del torneo y enviar el correo deben esperar respuesta y revisar si su nombre aparece en la lista de registros aceptados.\r\n\r\n*Para las personas provenientes de otros pases, registrarse y enviar un correo para coordinar el pago.\r\n\r\nEnglish\r\n\r\nPayment information:\r\nMake the respective payment, the cost is Q 110.00 base which includes participation in any event.\r\nIt also includes: T-shirt, credential and certificate of attendance. If you pay from september 30th and on, T-shirt will not be included.\r\n\r\nThe registration fee must be paid to the monetary bank account with number 3754007393, of Banrural with the name Adrin Ramrez. Next you must send an email with a photo of the receipt and name to cubeshopguatemala@gmail.com.\r\n\r\nAfter registering and sending the email, you have to wait for reply, and then chek if your name appears on the accepted registrations list.\r\n\r\n*For the people coming from other countries, please register and send an email to the same address to coordinate the payment.',0,NULL,0,1,0,0,0,NULL,'sta es una competencia conmemorativa en honor a haber cumplido 10 aos desde la primera competencia en el pas en Quetzaltenango 2023.\r\n\r\nThis is a commemorative competition in honor of having completed 10 years since our first competition in the country in Quetzaltenango 2023.',14573384,-90525865,'333','Dcimo Aniversario Guatemala 2023','This year is the tenth aniversary since our first competition in the country.',NULL,5500,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,'2023-10-13 22:00:00','2023-09-17 00:00:00','2023-09-16 01:00:15','remarks to the board here',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2023-10-14','2024-11-28 10:02:30',1,1,'[Colegio Car](https://care.edu.gt/)','23 calle 15-45, zona 13','','2023-10-13 23:10:00'),
