('10JohrWilerWurfelfast2024',1,0,'2024-02-11 00:42:36',19818,NULL,0,NULL,2000,NULL,NULL,'10 Johr Wiler Wrfelfst 2024','Wil SG',187,0,80,1,'Size of the venue.','2024-02-10 10:43:17',NULL,'','Switzerland','2024-02-06 07:41:27','CHF',0,NULL,0,'2024-03-24','2024-03-16 23:00:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',0,NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,NULL,'![](https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/dimension=684x10000:format=png/path/s3a9a136d3c2315ad/image/ibf8eb7faeef2afa2/version/1707248635/image.png)\ndeutsch\n Bitte beachte, dass du nur an einem der beiden Wettbewerbe teilnehmen kannst. Wenn du dich fr beide Wettbewerbe anmeldest, so zhlt nur die erste Anmeldung und wir werden die zweite (sptere) Anmeldung unverzglich lschen.\n\nenglish\nPlease note that you can only compete in one of the two competitions. If you register for both competitions, only the first registration will be valid and we will immediately delete the second (later) registration.\n\n\n',47463297,9041582,'333','10 Johr Wiler Wrfelfst 2024','10 Years Anniversary for this comp',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,'2024-03-16 20:00:00','2024-02-19 18:00:00','2024-02-18 18:00:02','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-04-01 07:55:13',229961,'2024-03-31 20:00:02',1,'2024-03-24','2024-04-01 07:55:13',1,1,'[Stadtsaal Wil](http://www.stadtsaal-wil.ch/)','Bahnhofplatz 6, 9500 Wil SG','Stadtsaal','2024-03-16 23:00:00'),
('10thAnniversaryCervantes2024',0,0,'2024-08-12 23:40:29',74269,NULL,0,NULL,30000,NULL,NULL,'10th Anniversary Cervantes 2024','Montevideo',NULL,1,40,1,'Venue size. 40 competitors + guests should be fine.','2024-08-12 13:55:48',NULL,'aus-competitions@googlegroups.com Instagram: @aus.uy','Uruguay','2024-08-10 00:42:48','UYU',0,NULL,0,'2024-09-15',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'##  Espaol\n\n## **LEER:**\n\n**COMPETIDORES NUEVOS**: deben leer [Importante](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/10thAnniversaryCervantes2024#47610-importante-read) y [Competidores nuevos](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/10thAnniversaryCervantes2024#47611-competidores-nuevos-newcomers).\n\n* Mximo **2** acompaante por persona.\n* El precio de la inscripcin es de $300.\n* No se reembolsar el dinero de la inscripcin bajo ningn concepto. En caso de haber realizado la transferencia, el pago quedar a favor del competidor para su inscripcin en una futura competencia, **solo si nos avisa con una semana de anticipacin o si el evento se cancela.**\n* Ante cualquier duda relacionada al pago de la inscripcin, contacte a la Asociacin Uruguaya de Speedcubing a travs de su pgina de Instagram [@aus.uy](https://www.instagram.com/aus.uy/) o por correo a aus-competitions@googlegroups.com.\n* **Ni los delegados de la WCA ni la organizacin del evento se harn responsables por transferencias que se realicen a cuentas equivocadas.**\n\n#### Pasos para inscribirse:\n1. Completar el registro siguiendo los pasos del tem \"Registro\" (Register).\n2. Si hay lugares libres, recibir un email\\* (puede demorar hasta 24 horas en llegar) con la informacin para pagar.\n3. Realice la transferencia.\n4. Responda al email que contiene la informacin para pagar (con la opcin \"responder a todos\") detallando **nombre/s** y **apellido/s** del competidor y adjuntando una copia del **comprobante** (en su versin electrnica o una foto del ticket), **sin esta informacin, el registro NO ser aceptado**.\n\n\\* El email lo recibir por parte de sofy.rojo18@gmail.com . Se sugiere revisar la direccin del email antes de realizar el pago.\n\n**Notas:**\n* Si el registro est completo, recomendamos a las personas con un registro pendiente que permanezcan alertas en caso de que se libere algn lugar.\n* En el caso de que no se alcance el lmite de competidores, se aceptarn las inscripciones in situ por orden de llegada.\n\n### **Al proceder con el registro, usted afirma haber ledo y estar de acuerdo con lo dicho en todos los apartados de este sitio web.**\n\n---\n\n##  English\n\n## **READ:**\n\n**NEW COMPETITORS**: You must read [Important](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/10thAnniversaryCervantes2024#47610-importante-read) and [New competitors](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/10thAnniversaryCervantes2024#47611-competidores-nuevos-newcomers).\n\n\n* Maximum **2** guests per competitor.\n* The registration price is $300.\n* The registration fee will not be refunded under any circumstances. If you have already made the bank transfer, the payment will remain in your favor for a future competition registration. In case you are unable to attend the competition, **you must notify us at least one week before the competition** in order to keep the payment for a future competition.\n* If you have any question, please contact the Asociacin Uruguaya de Speedcubing on Instagram [@aus.uy](https://www.instagram.com/aus.uy/) or by email to aus-competitions@googlegroups.com.\n* **Neither the WCA Delegates nor the organization team will be held responsible for transfers made to wrong bank accounts.**\n\n#### Registration procedure:\n1. Complete your registration by following the steps in the \"Register\" section.\n2. If there are spots available, you will receive an email\\* with the payment information (it may take up to 24 hours to arrive).\n3. Make the transfer.\n4. Reply-all to the email you received with the payment information, detailing **first name/s** and **last name/s** of the competitor and attaching a copy of the **bank transfer receipt** (in its electronic version or a photo of it), **without this information, the registration will NOT be accepted**. Once the transfer has been made, no refunds will be made under any circumstances, except for what has been said above.\n\n\\* You will receive the email from sofy.rojo18@gmail.com. You should check the email address before making the bank transfer.\n\n**Notes:**\n* If registration is full, we recommend people with a pending registration to remain alert in case a spot becomes available.\n* In the case of the competitor limit not being filled, on-the-spot registrations will be accepted in order of arrival at the venue.\n\n### By proceeding with the registration, you affirm that you have read and agree to the statements in all the sections of this website.',0,NULL,NULL,1,2,1,0,2,'![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBcElrIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--4be3c11536038145829dbcba17ca15bdea04981e/imagen.png)\n# ![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBaGxIIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--e1a87d9563999f890af638f98836b63b2aac90c5/6u.png) Espaol \nLmite de competidores: 40.\n\n* Leer el [Reglamento de la WCA](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/) para evitar posibles inconvenientes.\n* Esta competencia est abierta a competidores de cualquier nacionalidad, cualquier edad y a nuevos competidores, sin importar sus tiempos de resolucin.\n* **COMPETIDORES NUEVOS**: deben leer [Importante](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/10thAnniversaryCervantes2024#47610-importante-read) y [Competidores nuevos](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/10thAnniversaryCervantes2024#47611-competidores-nuevos-newcomers).\n* Los competidores deben llevar sus propios puzzles.\n* Los competidores deben estar presentes y listos para competir cuando se los llama.\n* Es importante leer toda la informacin disponible en la pgina de la competencia.\n\nAnte cualquier duda, consultar a los organizadores o a los delegados de la WCA.\n\n# ![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBaHBIIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--bacb00caed7d0c9177dc3ea7d687667b270ce30d/6i.png) English\nCompetitor limit: 40.\n\n* Read the [WCA Regulations](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/) to avoid any issue.\n* This competition is open to competitors of any nationality or age.\n* **NEW COMPETITORS**: You must read [Important](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/10thAnniversaryCervantes2024#47610-importante-read) and [New competitors](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/10thAnniversaryCervantes2024#47611-competidores-nuevos-newcomers).\n* Competitors must bring their own puzzles.\n* Competitors must be present and ready to compete when called.\n* It is important to read all the information available in the competition\'s website.\n\nFeel free to contact the organizers or the WCA Delegates.',-34895304,-56145318,'333','10th Anniversary Cervantes 2024','In 2024 it will be 10 years since the first competition in Uruguay, which was held in Cervantes (place where this competition will be held)',NULL,35000,1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,'2024-09-12 02:59:00','2024-08-17 00:00:00','2024-08-16 00:00:23','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-09-15 21:41:22',325394,'2024-09-15 21:34:40',1,'2024-09-14','2024-09-15 21:41:22',1,1,'[Colegio Cervantes](https://www.colegiocervantes.edu.uy/)','Maip 1751, 11600 Montevideo, Departamento de Montevideo','La competencia es en el anexo.','2024-09-14 00:00:00'),
