('15AnosSanSilvestre2024',0,0,'2024-06-03 08:01:47',118737,NULL,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'15 Aos San Silvestre 2024','Barrancabermeja',NULL,0,50,1,'The size of the venue','2024-06-03 04:38:39',NULL,'[Haiver Reyes](mailto:hgarcia@worldcubeassociation.org)','Colombia','2024-06-02 21:46:07','COP',0,NULL,0,'2024-07-07','2024-07-03 00:00:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'**REGISTRO**\nLa participacin en este torneo requiere de la comprensin de los siguientes requisitos:\n\nEl registro a esta competencia es gratis.\nConocer el reglamento de la WCA ya que este es un torneo oficial.\nElegir los eventos a inscribir cuidadosamente luego de revisar las pestaas Eventos y Cronograma. Prestar atencin a los formatos de las rondas y a sus cortes y lmites.\nEsperar a que el registro electrnico sea aceptado comunidandote al WhatsApp 3163611068.\n\n**REGISTRATION**\n\nParticipation in this tournament requires understanding of the following requirements:\n\nRegistration for this competition is free.\nFamiliarity with the WCA regulations as this is an official tournament.\nCarefully select the events to register for after reviewing the Events and Schedule tabs. Pay attention to the round formats and their cutoffs and limits.\nAwait electronic registration approval send to a WhatsApp messenger +57 3163611068  \n\n',0,NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,NULL,'Organizadores/Organizers:\n\nRafael Jimnez Cabrera\nCarlos Carreo\nHaiver Reyes\n\nPatrocinadores/Sponsors:\n\nCentro Comercial San Silvestre\nSpeedcubing Colombia\n![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbnQrIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--7d3a37e0c591748214f6708f0d2372dacd516b90/image.png)',7067333,-73857894,'333','15 Aos San Silvestre 2024','Name of the venue, the name of the mall is \"San Silvestre\" and it\'s the 15th anniversary of the mall.',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,'2024-07-03 00:00:00','2024-06-06 00:00:00','2024-06-05 00:00:17','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-