('1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024',1,0,'2024-01-03 14:43:04',74269,NULL,0,NULL,13000,NULL,NULL,'1:a Lrdagskuben i Vsters 2024','Vsters',NULL,1,50,1,'Venue and logistics.','2024-01-03 07:56:57',NULL,'[Email organizers](mailto:daniel.wallin@svekub.se;anton.lofberg@gmail.com;hewert@worldcubeassociation.org;phugossonmiller@worldcubeassociation.org)','Sweden','2024-01-02 08:19:13','SEK',0,'',1,'2024-02-03','2024-02-01 22:59:00',0,'',NULL,'',NULL,'## Anmlan\r\nFr att delta i tvlingen mste du anmla dig online [hr](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024/register) (scrolla lngst ner). Vi kommer inte acceptera ngra anmlningar p plats. Om du inte redan har ett WCA-konto, mste du frst skapa ett [hr](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/users/sign_up).\r\n\r\nAnmlan r inte komplett frrn anmlningsavgiften har betalats.\r\nAnmlan kostar 97,50 kr fr SveKub-medlemmar, 130 kr fr icke-medlemmar.\r\nAlla betalar fullt pris till att brja med, och vi betalar tillbaka 25% till de som r medlemmar.\r\nAtt bli medlem i SveKub r **gratis!** Ls mer [p vr hemsida](https://svekub.se/bli-medlem/) eller [bli medlem direkt](https://ebas.sverok.se/blimedlem/SveKub). Nr du registrerats som medlem kan du anmla dig till tvlingen som vanligt. Vi verifierar medlemskapet och terbetalar rabatten senast nr anmlan stngt.\r\n\r\nOm du inte finns med p [deltagarlistan](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024/registrations) inom 48 timmar frn anmlan, kontakta arrangrerna. (Kontaktuppgifter hittar du under \"General info\"-fliken.)\r\n\r\nOm du har anmlt dig men sedan inte lngre kan komma p tvlingen, mejla oss och informera om detta. Det ppnar upp din plats fr ngon annan.\r\n\r\nAnmlan stnger den 1:a februari, men tnk p att tvlingen kan bli fullsatt innan detta datum, i s fall hamnar din registrering p vntelistan. Notera att anmlningsavgiften mste betalas fr att du ska hamna p vntelistan, annars r anmlan inte komplett. Sista anmlningsdag r ocks sista dagen d det r mjligt f sin anmlan godknd ifrn vntelistan. r anmlan vid denna tidpunkt inte godknd finns tyvrr inte lngre ngon chans att delta p tvlingen, och du terbetalas hela anmlningsavgiften.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Registration\r\nTo attend this competition you need to register online [here](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024/register) (scroll to the bottom). We will not accept any registrations on the spot. If you don\'t already have a WCA-account, you first need to create one [here](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/users/sign_up).\r\n\r\nYour registration is not completed until the registration fee has been paid.\r\nThe registration fee is SEK 97,50 for members of SveKub, and SEK 130 for non-members.\r\nEveryone pays full price at first, and we will refund 25% to members.\r\nBecoming a member of SveKub is free, but only available for Swedish citizens. Read more on [our website](https://svekub.se/en/bli-medlem/) or [become a member now](https://ebas.sverok.se/blimedlem/SveKub). When you are registered as a member, you can register for the competition as normal. We verify the membership and refund the discount at latest once the registration period has ended. \r\n\r\nIf your name doesn\'t appear on the [competitor list](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/1aLordagskubeniVasteras2024/registrations) within 48 hours after registering, contact the organizers. (Contact information under the \"General info\" tab.)\r\n\r\nIf you have registered but then can\'t go to the competition, please send an e-mail telling us this as that will leave your spot for somebody else.\r\n\r\nOnline registration will close on February 1st, but please keep in mind that the competition may fill up earlier than that. In that case, your registration will be put on the waiting list. Note that the registration fee needs to be paid in order to be put on the waiting list, otherwise your registration is not completed. The last registration date is also the last date for when a registration can be accepted from the waiting. If your registration is not yet accepted by this date, then you will unfortunately not be able to compete at this competition, and will be refunded the entire registration fee.',0,NULL,0,1,0,1,0,NULL,'Vlkomna till 1:a Lrdagskuben i Vsters 2024!\r\n\r\nAlla r varmt vlkomna att delta, oavsett om du lser kuben p 5 sekunder eller 5 minuter samt oavsett tidigare tvlingserfarenhet.\r\n\r\nVi ber er lsa igenom alla flikar p denna sida eftersom de innehller mycket vrdefull information.\r\n\r\n--\r\n\r\nWelcome to 1:a Lrdagskuben i Vsters 2024!\r\n\r\nEveryone is welcome to participate, regardless of whether you solve the cube in 5 seconds or 5 minutes and regardless of prior competition experience.\r\n\r\nWe ask you to read through all the tabs on this page as they contain very valuable information.',59607616,16584644,'333','1:a Lrdagskuben i Vsters 2024','1st edition of the many upcoming Saturday competitions in this city in 2024.',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,'','2024-02-01 22:59:00',75,'2024-02-01 22:59:00','2024-01-06 18:00:00','2024-01-05 18:00:22','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-02-04 09:51:02',695,'2024-02-03 18:00:07',1,'2024-02-03','2024-02-04 09:51:02',1,1,'Viksngsskolan','Viksngsgatan 23, 723 47 Vsters','Matsalen','2024-02-01 22:59:00'),
