condiciones completamente diferentes a las habituales. Ser muy agotadora, y recomendamos pensar en si realmente podr completar la competencia. La competencia no se recomienda para nios pequeos ni para participantes completamente nuevos.\n\n\nNote: Please note that this is a very special competition with completely different conditions than usual. It will be very tiring, and we recommend thinking about whether you will actually be able to complete the competition. The competition is not recommended for younger children or for completely new participants. traduce a espanol',-2511812,-78927687,'333','24 Horas El Tambo 2024','This is the first edition of a 24-hour competition, El Tambo is the name of the city',NULL,600,1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,'2024-10-07 00:00:00','2024-08-25 00:00:00','2024-08-24 00:00:09','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-10-14 05:24:59',115116,'2024-10-14 00:06:07',1,'2024-10-12','2024-10-14 05:24:59',1,1,'Mishki Cafe','Carlos Pinos y Dositeo Gonzlez ','Cafeteria Mishki ','2024-10-07 00:00:00'),
('24HorasemSalvador2024',1,0,'2024-04-02 13:59:54',46413,NULL,0,NULL,5000,NULL,NULL,'24 Horas em Salvador 2024','Salvador, Bahia',NULL,1,40,1,'32 because we will have 8 stations, meaning at most four groups in a single event. Reallistically the venue could fit a 40 people competition, so if we see that the demand is big, we may want to increase the limit to 40 and use two more stations.','2024-04-01 22:46:31',NULL,'[Cubo Mgico Bahia](mailto:bahiacubomagico@gmail.com)','Brazil','2024-03-23 17:09:17','BRL',0,NULL,NULL,'2024-06-09','2024-06-05 02:59:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'O valor das inscries ser de R$ 50,00 a serem pagas de forma antecipada atravs da chave PIX: joaoszme@yahoo.com.br\n\n\nA inscrio s ser confirmada no site da WCA aps confirmao do pagamento e envio do comprovante para o e-mail do [Cubo Mgico Bahia](bahiacubomagico@gmail.com).\n\n\nRegistration fee will be R$ 50,00 (Brazilian Real) to be paid in advance using the PIX key: joaoszme@yahoo.com.br\n\nRegistration will only be confirmed on the WCA website after payment confirmation with a proof of transfer sent to the organizer\'s email [Cubo Mgico Bahia](bahiacubomagico@gmail.com).',0,NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,NULL,'![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBclp5IiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--3eb495a7327c9da34d21481bc68870f97c1e03ae/image.png)\n\nInscrio de competidor: R$ 50,00\n**Por se tratar de um local com tamanho limitado, ser permitido apenas um convidado por competidor, sem a possibilidade de adio de novos convidados** \nLimite de competidores: 40\n\n\nRegistration fee: R$ 50,00\n**As the venue has a limited size, it will be permitted a single guest per competitor, without any possibility of the addition of other guests.**\nCompetitor limit: 40\n\n\nREGISTRO\nA participao nessa competio requer do competidor o conhecimento dos seguintes requisitos, sem o cumprimento destes, a inscrio no ser aceita:\n\nEstar familiarizado com o Regulamento da WCA;\nSe inscrever atravs do site da WCA, realizar o pagamento de forma antecipada e mandar o comprovante para o organizador atravs do e-mail (bahiacubomagico@gmail.com) indicando o nome completo do participante. Detalhes sobre o pagamento da inscrio abaixo.\n\nAguardar at que o registro eletrnico seja aceito. Caso no participe mesmo com o pagamento, no haver devoluo do dinheiro. \nH um limite de 40 competidores\nOutras informaes adicionais verifique no site da WCA ou entre em contato com o organizador atravs do e-mail (bahiacubomagico@gmail.com).\n\nPara os competidores menores de idade que forem ficar desacompanhados durante o perodo da noite, ser necessrio o envio de uma autorizao de um pai ou responsvel autorizando a permanncia aps este horrio.\n\nEsta  uma competio de 24 horas e portanto atente-se a isso. Caso no possa ficar as 24 horas, no h necessidade, preze pela sua sade e bem-estar mental.\n\nREGISTRATION\nThe participation in this competition requires the comprehension and acceptance of the following requirements, without fulfilling these requirements, the registration will not be accepted:\n\nRegister through the WCA website, pay in advance and send proof to the organizer via email (bahiacubomagico@gmail.com) indicating the participant\'s full name. More details about the payment below;\n\nWait for your registration to be approved online. In the case of not participating and having already paid the registration, no money will be returned. \nThere will be a limit of 40 competitors.\nFor additional information, check the WCA website or contact the organizer via email, (bahiacubomagico@gmail.com)\n\nTo underage competitors that will stay alone during the night period, it will be requested an express authorization of a parent or guardian authorizing the competitor\'s participation during said period.\n\nThis is a 24 hour competition, therefore, be attentive to that. In case you\'re not able to stay the 24 hours, there is no need to, value your health and mental well-being.',-12943067,-38338084,'333','24 Horas em Salvador 2024','It is going to be a 24 hour competition happening in Salvador in 2024',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,'2024-06-01 02:59:00','2024-04-20 03:00:00','2024-04-19 03:00:20','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-06-11 05:47:57',65975,'2024-06-10 19:32:44',1,'2024-06-08','2024-06-11 05:47:57',1,1,'Residncia Privada em Stella Maris','Stella Maris','O endereo completo ser enviado aos competidores registrados assim que as inscries fecharem.','2024-06-05 02:59:00'),
('24HoursinAker2024',1,1,'2024-04-20 20:23:13',118737,NULL,0,NULL,13000,NULL,NULL,'24 Hours in ker 2024','kers Styckebruk',NULL,1,50,1,'Venue size, logistics and schedule constraints.','2024-04-20 12:42:45',NULL,'[Organization Team](mailto:helmer.ewert@svekub.se)','Sweden','2024-04-18 16:50:59','SEK',0,NULL,1,'2024-07-07','2024-07-04 21:59:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'## Anmlan\nFr att delta i tvlingen mste du anmla dig online [hr](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/24HoursinAker2024/register) (scrolla lngst ner). Vi kommer inte acceptera ngra anmlningar p plats. Om du inte redan har ett WCA-konto, mste du frst skapa ett [hr](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/users/sign_up).\n\nAnmlan r inte komplett frrn anmlningsavgiften har betalats.\nAnmlan kostar 97,50 kr fr SveKub-medlemmar, 130 kr fr icke-medlemmar.\nAlla betalar fullt pris till att brja med, och vi betalar tillbaka 25% till de som r medlemmar.\nAtt bli medlem i SveKub r **gratis!** Ls mer [p vr hemsida](https://svekub.se/bli-medlem/) eller [bli medlem direkt](https://ebas.sverok.se/blimedlem/SveKub). Nr du registrerats som medlem kan du anmla dig till tvlingen som vanligt. Vi verifierar medlemskapet och terbetalar rabatten senast nr anmlan stngt.\n\nOm du inte finns med p [deltagarlistan](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/24HoursinAker2024/registrations) inom 48 timmar frn anmlan, kontakta arrangrerna. (Kontaktuppgifter hittar du under \"General info\"-fliken.)\n\nOm du har anmlt dig men sedan inte lngre kan komma p tvlingen, mejla oss och informera om detta. Det ppnar upp din plats fr ngon annan.\n\nAnmlan stnger den 4:e juli, men tnk p att tvlingen kan bli fullsatt innan detta datum, i s fall hamnar din registrering p vntelistan. Notera att anmlningsavgiften mste betalas fr att du ska hamna p vntelistan, annars r anmlan inte komplett. Sista anmlningsdag r ocks sista dagen d det r mjligt f sin anmlan godknd ifrn vntelistan. r anmlan vid denna tidpunkt inte godknd finns tyvrr inte lngre ngon chans att delta p tvlingen, och du terbetalas hela anmlningsavgiften.\n\n---\n\n## Registration\nTo attend this competition you need to register online [here](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/24HoursinAker2024/register) (scroll to the bottom). We will not accept any registrations on the spot. If you don\'t already have a WCA-account, you first need to create one [here](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/users/sign_up).\n\nYour registration is not completed until the registration fee has been paid.\nThe registration fee is SEK 97,50 for members of SveKub, and SEK 130 for non-members.\nEveryone pays full price at first, and we will refund 25% to members.\nBecoming a member of SveKub is free, but only available for Swedish citizens. Read more on [our website](https://svekub.se/en/bli-medlem/) or [become a member now](https://ebas.sverok.se/blimedlem/SveKub). When you are registered as a member, you can register for the competition as normal. We verify the membership and refund the discount at latest once the registration period has ended. \n\nIf your name doesn\'t appear on the [competitor list](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/24HoursinAker2024/registrations) within 48 hours after registering, contact the organizers. (Contact information under the \"General info\" tab.)\n\nIf you have registered but then can\'t go to the competition, please send an e-mail telling us this as that will leave your spot for somebody else.\n\nOnline registration will close on July 4th, but please keep in mind that the competition may fill up earlier than that. In that case, your registration will be put on the waiting list. Note that the registration fee needs to be paid in order to be put on the waiting list, otherwise your registration is not completed. The last registration date is also the last date for when a registration can be accepted from the waiting. If your registration is not yet accepted by this date, then you will unfortunately not be able to compete at this competition, and will be refunded the entire registration fee.',0,NULL,NULL,1,1,1,0,NULL,'Varmt vlkomna till denna 24-timmarstvling i kers Styckebruk! \n\nPrecis som vanligt s r alla som nskar varmt vlkomna att delta, men vi vill nd utfrda en kraftig varning kring att tvlingen pgr nonstop i just 24 timmar, och har ett vldigt speciellt koncept. Drfr passar tvlingen sannolikt inte varken nya eller yngre deltagare srskilt bra. Ls grna igenom alla flikar p denna sida s du inte missar ngon viktig information, srskilt fliken [koncept](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/24HoursinAker2024#43667-koncept-concept).\n\n-----\n\nA warm welcome to this 24-hour competition in kers Styckebruk! \n\nJust as usual, everyone who wishes is warmly welcome to participate, but we still want to issue a strong warning that the competition runs non-stop for exactly 24 hours, and has a very special concept. Therefore, the competition probably does not suit neither new or younger participants very well. Please read through all the tabs on this page so you don\'t miss any important information, especially the [concept tab](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/24HoursinAker2024#43667-koncept-concept).\n\n[![](https://cuboss.se/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/cuboss-svekub-loggor.png)](https://svekub.se/om_oss/svekub-cuboss/)',59253315,17097545,'333','24 Hours in ker 2024','Constant competing for 24 hours, and a shortened name of the town, because using the full one would be over 32 characters. The shortened one is commonly used by people in the area.',NULL,20000,0,NULL,0,NULL,'2024-07-04 21:59:00',75,'2024-07-04 21:59:00','2024-04-24 17:00:00','2024-04-23 17:00:04','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-07-07 14:39:40',9217,'2024-07-07 13:05:04',1,'2024-07-06','2024-07-07 14:39:40',1,1,'[Folkets Hus](https://www.strangnas.se/uppleva-och-gora/motesplatser/motesplats-akers-styckebruk)','Torget 1, 647 51 kers Styckebruk','','2024-07-04 21:59:00'),
('24HoursinFlen2023',1,0,'2023-05-16 21:00:43',52559,NULL,0,NULL,40000,NULL,NULL,'24 Hours in Flen 2023','Flen',NULL,1,24,1,'Venue size and logistics.','2023-05-16 20:29:43',NULL,'[Email organizers](mailto:daniel.wallin@svekub.se;viktor.zenk@svekub.se)','Sweden','2023-04-29 20:41:49','SEK',0,'',1,'2023-07-23','2023-07-20 21:59:00',0,'',NULL,'',NULL,'## Anmlan\r\nFr att delta i tvlingen mste du anmla dig online. Vi kommer inte acceptera ngra anmlningar p plats. Om du inte redan har ett WCA-konto, mste du frst skapa ett [hr](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/users/sign_up).\r\n\r\nAnmlan r inte komplett frrn anmlningsavgiften har betalats.\r\nAnmlan kostar 300 kr fr SveKub-medlemmar, 400 kr fr icke-medlemmar. Sngplats (vandrarhemsstandard) ver natten ingr i priset. Alla betalar fullt pris till att brja med, och vi betalar tillbaka 25% till de som r medlemmar. Vi verifierar medlemskapet i samband med att anmlan granskas (godknns eller stts p vntelistan). Att bli medlem i SveKub r **gratis!** Ls mer [p vr hemsida](https://svekub.se/bli-medlem/) eller [registrera dig direkt](https://ebas.sverok.se/blimedlem/SveKub).\r\n\r\nOm du inte finns med p [deltagarlistan](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/24HoursinFlen2023/registrations) inom 24 timmar frn anmlan, kontakta arrangrerna. (Kontaktuppgifter hittar du under \"General info\"-fliken.)\r\n\r\nOm du har anmlt dig men sedan inte lngre kan komma p tvlingen, maila oss och informera om detta. Det ppnar upp din plats fr ngon annan.\r\n\r\nAnmlan stnger den 20:e juli, men tnk p att tvlingen kan bli fullsatt innan detta datum, i s fall hamnar din registrering p vntelistan. Notera att anmlningsavgiften mste betalas fr att du ska hamna p vntelistan, annars r anmlan inte komplett. I detta fall gller samma datum som sista dag fr att f sin anmlan godknd ifrn vntelistan. r anmlan vid denna tidpunkt inte godknd finns tyvrr inte lngre ngon chans att delta p tvlingen, och du terbetalas hela anmlningsavgiften.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Registration\r\nTo attend this competition you need to register online. We will not accept any registrations on the spot. If you don\'t already have a WCA-account, you first need to create one [here](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/users/sign_up).\r\n\r\nYour registration is not completed until the registration fee has been paid.\r\nThe registration fee is 300 SEK for members of SveKub, and 400 SEK for non-members. A hostel style bed is included in the prize. Everyone pays full price at first, and we will then refund 25% to members. We verify the membership when reviewing the registration (approving it or moving it to the waiting list). Becoming a member of SveKub is free, but only available for Swedish citizens. Read more on [our website](https://svekub.se/en/bli-medlem/) or [register right away](https://ebas.sverok.se/blimedlem/SveKub).\r\n\r\nIf your name doesn\'t appear on the [competitor list](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/24HoursinFlen2023/registrations) within 24 hours after registering, contact the organizers. (Contact information under the \"General info\" tab.)\r\n\r\nIf you have registered but then can\'t go to the competition, please send an e-mail telling us this as that will leave your spot for somebody else.\r\n\r\nOnline registration will close on July 20th, but please keep in mind that the competition may fill up earlier than that. In that case, your registration will be put on the waiting list. Note that the registration fee needs to be paid in order to be put on the waiting list, otherwise your registration is not completed. The same date is also the last date for when a registration can be moved from the waiting list to the competitors list. If your registration is not yet approved by this date, then you will unfortunately not be able to compete at this competition, and will be refunded the entire registration fee.',0,NULL,0,1,0,1,30000,NULL,'Varmt vlkomna till denna 24-timmarstvling i Flen! Precis som vanligt 