('2x2CubeMastersBogota2023',0,0,'2023-09-21 16:32:16',177722,NULL,0,NULL,2500000,NULL,NULL,'2x2 Cube Masters Bogot 2023','Bogot',NULL,0,100,1,'The size of the venue.','2023-09-21 16:31:07',NULL,'[Juan Camilo Gonzlez](mailto:camilationtgmaes@gmail.com)','Colombia','2023-09-21 13:39:43','COP',0,'',0,'2023-11-26','2023-11-25 19:00:00',0,'',NULL,'',NULL,'REGISTRO\r\nLa participacin en este torneo requiere de la comprensin de los siguientes requisitos:\r\n1.	El valor de la inscripcin para uno o todos los eventos es de $25.000 pesos Colombianos\r\n2.	Conocer el reglamento de la WCA ya que este es un torneo oficial.\r\n3.	Elegir los eventos a inscribir cuidadosamente luego de revisar las pestaas Eventos y Cronograma. Prestar atencin a los formatos de las rondas y a sus cortes y lmites.\r\n4.	Inscribirse electrnicamente completando el proceso aqu.\r\n5.	Hacer el pago de la inscripcin a la cuenta de Nequi #3227344666\r\n6.	Enviar comprobante de pago al Whatsapp # 3227344666 con el nombre completo del participante ya registrado en la WCA en el torneo.\r\n7.	Esperar a que el registro electrnico sea aceptado.\r\n8.	!Divertirse!\r\nREGISTRATION\r\nThe participation in this competition requires the comprehension and acceptance of the following requirements:\r\n1.	Registration fee for one or all events is $25.000 Colombian Pesos.\r\n2.	Being familiar with the WCA rules since this is an official competition.\r\n3.	Carefully choosing the events. Keep the rounds format, cutoffs and limits in mind.\r\n4.	Registering online completing the process here.\r\n5.	Paying your registration to Nequi account #3227344666\r\n6.	Sending a screenshot or an image of the receipt through WhatsApp to the number 3227344666 with the competitors full name after he/she is already registered on the competition website.\r\n7.	Waiting for your registration to be approved online.\r\n8.	Have fun!\r\n',0,NULL,0,1,0,1,0,NULL,'Organizadores/Organizers:\r\n\r\nJuan Camilo Gonzlez Barragn\r\nSpeedcubing Colombia\r\n\r\nPatrocinadores/Sponsors:\r\n\r\nEdurubiks',4601995,-74157221,'222','2x2 Cube Masters Bogot 2023','The main event will be 2x2x2.',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,'2023-11-24 19:00:00','2023-09-24 14:00:00','2023-09-23 14:00:08','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2023-11-27 09:45:03',9217,'2023-11-27 00:47:23',1,'2023-11-26','2023-11-27 09:45:03',1,1,'Saln Comunal Villa del Ro','Calle 55A sur # 66-50','Primer piso','2023-11-25 19:00:00'),
('2x2inaMadisonLodge2022',1,0,'2022-10-21 13:52:44',6777,NULL,0,NULL,3500,NULL,NULL,'2x2 in a Madison Lodge 2022','Madison, Wisconsin',NULL,0,160,1,'Room size','2022-10-21 04:03:21',NULL,'','USA','2022-10-11 15:10:07','USD',0,'',1,'2022-12-03','2022-11-27 05:59:00',0,'',NULL,'',NULL,'## Registration Process\r\n\r\n1. Wait until registration opens on  **October 26, 2022 8:00 PM CDT**. You cannot register prior to then. You cannot register after **November 27, 2022 at 11:59 PM CST**. No exceptions to these will be given.\r\n2. If you have not competed before, create a WCA account [here](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/users/sign_up)\r\n3. Go to the [**Register**](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/2x2inaMadisonLodge2022/register) link on the competition website.\r\n4. Fill out the events you will be competing in,  any comments you may have about your registration, and press register.\r\n5. Pay the registration fee via Stripe on the competition website.\r\n\r\n#### Competitors MUST pay their registration fee before being eligible for a spot in the competition.\r\n\r\n\r\n## Waitlist\r\n\r\nIf the competition is full, a message will be displayed saying such on the competition website. If, after this time, you register and pay for the competition, you will be added to the competition waitlist. \r\n\r\nIf a competitor cancels their registration, the person at the top of the waitlist will be added to the competitor list.\r\n\r\nIf you are on the waitlist, you may cancel your registration (see below) at any time for a full refund.\r\n\r\nIf you are on the waitlist, you will be informed whether you have made it on the competitor list after **November 27, 2022 at 11:59 PM CST**, otherwise you will be given a full refund.\r\n\r\n## Registration Changes\r\n\r\nIf you would like to cancel your registration, email the [organization team](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/contact/website?competitionId=2x2inaMadisonLodge2022) with your request and you will be refunded **80%** of your registration fee. Refunds are available only until **November 27, 2022 at 11:59 PM CST**\r\n\r\nIf you would like to edit your registered events or listed guests, you may do so on the [Register](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/2x2inaMadisonLodge2022/register) page. This can only be done prior to **November 27, 2022 at 11:59 PM CST**.',0,NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,NULL,'While 2x2 is the main event of this competition, 3x3 is still featured. We hope you\'ll join us in Madison this December!\r\n',43077407,-89386762,'222','2x2 in a Madison Lodge 2022','There is 2x2 in a lodge in Madison in 2022',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,'','2022-11-27 05:59:00',80,'2022-11-27 05:59:00','2022-10-27 01:00:00','2022-10-26 01:00:10','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2022-12-04 05:59:00',24542,'2022-12-04 05:04:42',1,'2022-12-03','2022-12-04 05:59:00',1,1,'Wisconsin Masonic Center','301 Wisconsin Ave, Madison, WI 53703','Grand Ballroom','2022-11-27 05:59:00'),
