('50thAnniversaryinElverum2024',1,0,'2024-04-16 13:09:24',46413,NULL,0,NULL,17500,NULL,NULL,'50th Anniversary in Elverum 2024','Elverum',NULL,0,50,1,'Venue Space','2024-04-16 12:28:05',NULL,'','Norway','2024-04-03 19:32:36','NOK',0,NULL,1,'2024-05-19',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'###  Registrering\nHver registrerte deltaker m godkjennes manuelt av arrangrene. Etter at dette har blitt gjort, vil deltakeren motta en e-post med bekreftelse. Vennligst ta kontakt du ikke er p lista innen 48 timer. Nye deltakere minnes om at de m ta med legitimasjon.\n\n### NKF Medlemmer\nMedlemmer av Norges Kubeforbund vil f 50kr av registreringsavgiften refundert etter konkurransen. Instruksjoner for  melde seg inn finnes p NKF sin [hjemmeside](https://kubing.no/omoss).\n\n### Personvern\nDet kommer til  bli tatt bde bilder og video p dette arrangementet, bde i privat regi, og p vegne av Norges Kubeforbund. Ved  delta p dette arrangementet aksepterer du at bilder og eller video av deg kan bli brukt av Norges Kubeforbund eller andre aktrer.\n\n---\n\n###  Information\nEach registered competitor has to be manually accepted by the organization team. After this is done, a confirmation email is sent to the competitor. Please contact us if you\'ve not been accepted after 48 hours. New competitors are reminded to bring some form of ID to the competition.\n\n### NKF Members\nMembers of Norges Kubeforbund will get 50 NOK refunded after the competition. Instuctions on how to become a member can be found on the NKF [website](https://kubing.no/omoss).\n\n### Privacy Disclaimer\nFilming and photography will be prevalent at this competition, both privately and on behalf of Norges Kubeforbund. By attending you consent that your likeness may be used in the form of video and/or photos.',0,NULL,NULL,1,1,1,0,NULL,'This competition is open to everyone who wants to participate.',60881594,11564437,'333','50th Anniversary in Elverum 2024','Held in Elverum',NULL,17500,1,NULL,0,NULL,'2024-05-16 00:00:00',75,'2024-05-16 00:00:00','2024-04-27 00:00:00','2024-04-26 00:00:08','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-05-22 04:48:59',65975,'2024-05-21 21:26:01',1,'2024-05-18','2024-05-22 04:48:59',1,1,'Ungdommens Hus','St. Olavs Gate 6, 2414 Elverum','We will use the main room','2024-05-16 00:00:00'),
('50thAnniversaryinIndo2024',0,0,'2024-11-08 17:14:40',177722,NULL,0,NULL,10000000,NULL,NULL,'50th Anniversary in Indo 2024','Jakarta',NULL,0,110,1,'Organizers capability','2024-11-08 10:24:07',NULL,'Kenneth: +628119823301 or Cendy: +6283869962288 ','Indonesia','2024-10-29 06:07:05','IDR',0,NULL,NULL,'2024-12-07','2024-12-07 06:00:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'# English\nRegistration Fee:\n1-2 Events: Rp100.000\nAll Events : Rp150.000\nOn the Spot Registration (3x3 only) : Rp150.000\n\nFree registration fee for Rapid Academy students.\n\nRegistration Requirements:\n1. Fill the online registration form on the Register tab, choose the events you want to participate, and click the Register! button.\n2. Pay the registration fee via bank transfer to blu by BCA Digital: 002217085677 Kenneth Emanuel Nursalim\n3. Confirm your registration payment by filling out [this form](https://forms.gle/noqotNVdWfzqX2cg7)\n4. Your registration will only be accepted and considered complete once the online registration has been submitted, and both payment and confirmation have been successfully made. Please wait for the registration to be approved. If the registration has not been approved after 1x24 hours after filling the form, please let the organizers know.\n\n# Bahasa Indonesia\nBiaya Pendaftaran:\n1-2 Events: Rp100.000\nAll Events : Rp150.000\nRegistration Ditempat (hanya 3x3) : Rp150.000\n\nGratis biaya registrasi untuk murid Rapid Academy.\n\nProsedur Pendaftaran:\n1. Lakukan registrasi dengan mengisi registrasi online pada tab register, pilih event yang ingin diikuti, dan klik tombol Register!\n2. Lakukan pembayaran registrasi melalui transfer bank blu by BCA Digital: 002217085677 Kenneth Emanuel Nursalim\n3. Lakukan konfirmasi pembayaran dengan mengisi [form ini](https://forms.gle/noqotNVdWfzqX2cg7)\n4. Registrasi hanya akan diterima dan dianggap selesai bila sudah melakukan mengisi registrasi online, melakukan pembayaran dan mengisi form konfirmasi pembayaran. Harap menunggu untuk registrasi diterima. Apabila registrasi anda masih belum diterima 1x24 jam setelah mengisi form, mohon hubungi tim organizer segera untuk dicek kembali.',0,NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,NULL,'This competition is held in collaboration with Rapid Academy and the Embassy of Hungary in Indonesia to celebrate the 50th anniversary of one of the Hungarian inventions, Rubik\'s Cube.\n\nThere will be a cash prize for this competition from our sponsors, and also a special prize from Rubiks (Toyspedia): Rubiks 50th Anniversary Special Edition!\n\nThis competition is free for all Rapid Academy students.\n____\n\nPerlombaan ini diadakan bersama dengan Rapid Academy dan Kedutaan Besar Hongaria di Indonesia untuk merayakan 50 tahun salah satu ciptaan Hongaria, Rubik\'s Cube.\n\nAkan ada hadiah berupa uang tunai untuk kompetisi ini dari para sponsor, serta hadiah spesial dari Rubik\'s (Toyspedia): Rubik\'s 50th Anniversary Special Edition!\n\nKompetisi ini gratis untuk seluruh murid Rapid Academy.',-6190357,106838534,'333','50th Anniversary in Indonesia 2024','In collaboration with the embassy of hungary, This event celebrate the 50th anniversary of Rubik\'s Cube',NULL,15000000,1,NULL,0,NULL,'2024-11-30 00:00:00',0,'2024-11-30 00:00:00','2024-11-11 00:00:00','2024-11-10 00:00:21','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-12-13 17:35:47',156865,'2024-12-13 17:16:13',1,'2024-12-07','2024-12-13 17:35:47',1,1,'Taman Ismail Marzuki','Jl. Cikini Raya No.8, Cikini, Menteng, Central Jakarta City, Jakarta 10330','Galeri Cipta 2 (3rd Floor)','2024-12-06 00:00:00'),
('50YearsofCubingBulgaria2024',1,0,'2024-04-10 11:12:35',46413,NULL,0,NULL,1500,NULL,NULL,'50 Years of Cubing Bulgaria 2024','Sofia',NULL,0,100,1,'Venue size is enough for 100 competitors and about 150 guests.','2024-04-10 09:42:55',NULL,NULL,'Bulgaria','2024-04-03 18:40:38','BGN',0,NULL,NULL,'2024-05-12','2024-05-03 10:00:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'          .       !\n\n    ,     2 :\n1)  (   48 )   e-mail,   .  e-mail         , 2   .\n2)       15  ( 30   2- )  ,    .     12:00     .\n3)                5   .     12:00     .\n\n*    ,        e-mail,       .\n*    e-mail,         ,    ,  ,           ,          .\n\n-----------\n\nThe competition is part of Hungarian week in Techno magic land. We have prepared great surprises for all competitors!\n\nTo complete your registration you have to do two things:\n1) Confirm your spot by answering in 48 hours at the confirmation mail that we will send two weeks before the competition.\n2) Pay the 15 leva (or 30 leva for the 2 days) registration fee at the venue until 12:00.\n3) Spectators can attend by paying the fee for Guests which is 5 lv per day, collected at the venue until 12:00.\n\n*If the limit will be reached and you didn\'t reply to the confirmation mail you will be deleted from the registration list.\n*If you confirm your spot on email but didn\'t register at the venue before your very first event will consider that you will not come anymore and will accept someone else.',0,NULL,NULL,1,1,1,500,NULL,'   1    .                 5 /.         ,      .              .\n     : 1784 . , .   111,  \"\" -   \n\n----------\n\nMaximum 1 guest per competitor. The fee for Guests and Spectators to be paid in the venue on the day of the competition and is 5lv/day. Registration fee to be paid in the venue on the day of the competition. You can choose on which day of the competition you will participate or both.\nThe address of Techno Magic Land is: 111B Tsarigradsko shose, \"Experimentarium\" hall - Sofia Tech Park.',42665807,23373