('5BLDMastersOpole2025',0,1,'2025-01-16 15:01:40',19818,NULL,0,NULL,6000,NULL,NULL,'5BLD Masters Opole 2025','Opole',NULL,1,30,1,'Venue size and safety measures.','2025-01-15 18:00:41',NULL,'[Karol Zakrzewski](mailto:kzakrzewski@worldcubeassociation.org)','Poland','2024-12-18 10:46:03','PLN',0,NULL,0,'2025-03-02','2025-02-24 18:00:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'![](https://i.imgur.com/y4aZ08M.png) **Polski:**\nUWAGA: W konkurencji 3x3x3 Multiblind obowizuje oddzielny 20-osobowy limit zawodnikw.\nAby pojawi si na licie zawodnikw / rezerwowej musisz wej w zakadk \"Zarejestruj si\" widoczn po lewej stronie/na grze, wypeni formularz rejestracyjny i **opaci wpisowe** przed upywem czasu wyznaczonego przez formularz. Akceptacja zawodnikw, ktrzy opacili wpisowe, **NIE jest automatyczna** - moe ona potrwa do 72 godzin od opacenia zgoszenia.\nWypeniajc formularz, zgadzasz si na publikowanie i uywanie Twojego wizerunku w mediach spoecznociowych przez organizatorw, zawodnikw, goci i sponsorw turnieju. Dotyczy to zdj i nagra wykonanych podczas trwania turnieju.\n\n------\n![](https://i.imgur.com/i1ldA95.png) **English:**\nNOTE: In 3x3x3 MBLD, there is also a separate 20-person competitor limit.\nIn order to appear on competitor / waiting list you need to go to \"Register\" tab, which you can find on the left, submit a registration form and **pay your registration fee**. Competitors who paid the entry fee are being **accepted manually**, so you will have to wait up to 72 hours to get accepted.\nWhen submitting your registration you agree on publishing and using your image in social media by organisers, competitors, guests and sponsors of the competition. This includes photos and recordings done at the competition.',0,NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,0,'![](https://i.imgur.com/y4aZ08M.png) **Polski:** Serdecznie zapraszamy do Opola na prawdziwy spektakl mistrzw 5BLD!\n\n\n-----------------------\n![](https://i.imgur.com/i1ldA95.png) **English:** Come to Opole and see the real 5BLD Masters!\n\n![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsiZGF0YSI6NjA5MDMsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--114ff2b38ee1e3f8aae57d5390722155ddacee86/5bldmasterslogo.png)\n',50682163,17869058,'555bf','5BLD Masters Opole 2025','Competition is taking place in Opole city. The main event is 5bld therefore it is mentioned in the name.',NULL,6000,0,NULL,0,NULL,'2025-02-24 18:00:00',95,'2025-02-24 18:00:00','2025-02-04 18:00:00','2025-02-03 18:00:24','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2025-03-02 17:00:28',20805,'2025-03-02 16:45:56',1,'2025-03-01','2025-03-02 17:00:28',1,1,'Wojewdzki Inspektorat Weterynarii','Wrocawska 170, 46-020 Opole','Assembly hall','2025-02-24 18:00:00'),
('5thGuwahatiOpen2019',0,0,'2019-11-28 15:44:16',1284,NULL,0,NULL,35000,NULL,NULL,'5th Guwahati Open 2019','Guwahati, Assam',NULL,0,100,1,'Organizing team\'s manpower is a bit lower than year\'s past. We are reasonably expecting 100 participants maximum as the venue is quite small. ','2019-11-27 14:51:01',NULL,'','India','2019-11-23 10:59:07','INR',0,'',0,'2019-12-29',NULL,0,'',NULL,'',NULL,'**Register online**\r\nPay the registration fee using the link available in the Payment tab.\r\n\r\n**Steps to register on spot:**\r\nSpot registration will be open the whole day on Dec 28 2019 for events that haven\'t started by the time you register. and upto 10:00 a.m on Dec 29 2019.\r\n\r\nNote: There will be no spot registration if online registration reaches 100 participants. Also, spot registration will be closed once the total registration reaches 100. \r\n\r\n**Registration fee**\r\nBase fee (for participating): 300\r\nEach event: 50\r\nSo if you are participating in 3 events, fees will be 300 + (3x50) = 450.\r\n\r\n',0,NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,NULL,'All the participants are requested to volunteer in the competition and every participant (except New comers) will be assigned to a particular event they have to Judge (or) Scramble in which they are participating, all this will be decided by the organising team.we will make sure that your volunteering will not affect your events.\r\nAdditional information will be provided in the tabs.\r\nPlease bring your ID cards for identification at the venue.\r\n\r\n\r\n',26187422,91746736,'333','5th Guwahati Open 2019','We already have 4 editions of Guwahati and now this is 5th',NULL,35000,1,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,'2019-12-25 15:30:00','2019-12-01 00:00:00','2019-11-30 00:00:09','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2020-01-01 13:32:02',2,'2019-12-31 07:18:43',1,'2019-12-28','2020-01-01 13:32:02',1,1,'Cotton University','Pan Bazar, Guwahati, Assam 781001','Philosophy department ground floor ',NULL),
