('6thGuwahatiOpen2024',0,0,'2024-08-14 00:14:35',177722,NULL,0,NULL,30000,NULL,NULL,'6th Guwahati Open 2024','Guwahati, Assam',NULL,0,111,1,'Space constraints','2024-08-13 20:40:46',NULL,'speedcubingguwahati@gmail.com','India','2024-08-08 04:25:21','INR',0,NULL,NULL,'2024-09-22','2024-09-18 18:29:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'## [CLICK HERE FOR REGISTRATION AND PAYMENT PROCEDURE](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/6thGuwahatiOpen2024#47691-registration-and-payment)\n\n**Notes:**\n**1.** It is mandatory to **pay the registration fees** AND **register on WCA** to complete the full registration process.\n**2.** Wait for upto 48 hours to get your registration confirmed after payment has been done.\n**3.** If you are a first time participant, please bring a valid goverment ID proof (Aadhaar, Passport etc) for verification.\n**4.** For the returning participants: Please claim your WCA ID if you have not claimed it yet. [Click here for tutorial video.](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3widl70-Uus&ab_channel=GeoCuber)\n**5.** Please check your respective mail ID\'s through which you will receive all the communications from the organisation team.',0,NULL,0,1,2,1,0,2,'* Make sure to be available at the venue at least 15 minutes before your event starts. Late entries won\'t be allowed to participate.\n* Attend the new participates tutorial session if you\'re new to WCA competitions or unfamiliar with its rules.\n* Bring a Government ID card for verification if it\'s your first time participating in a WCA competition.\n* Participants are expected to volunteer and will be assigned with roles as judges, scramblers, or runners, with the exception of newcomers.',26185956,91772139,'333','6th Guwahati Open 2024','6th edition of this competition to be held in the city of Guwahati.',NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,'2024-09-16 18:29:00','2024-08-18 03:30:00','2024-08-17 04:00:10','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2024-09-26 21:00:19',259132,'2024-09-26 20:44:23',1,'2024-09-21'