('70AnosFatimaMontevideo2025',1,0,'2025-05-01 11:32:39',234900,NULL,0,NULL,30000,NULL,NULL,'70 Aos Ftima Montevideo 2025','Montevideo',NULL,0,40,1,'Estimated venue space.','2025-04-30 14:14:52',NULL,'aus-competitions@googlegroups.com Instagram: [@aus.uy](https://www.instagram.com/aus.uy/)','Uruguay','2025-04-24 19:33:18','UYU',0,NULL,0,'2025-06-01','2025-06-01 02:59:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'# ![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBaGxIIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--e1a87d9563999f890af638f98836b63b2aac90c5/6u.png) Espaol \n\n## **LEER:**\n\n**COMPETIDORES NUEVOS**: deben leer [Importante](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/70AnosFatimaMontevideo2025#59119-importante-read) y [Competidores nuevos](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/70AnosFatimaMontevideo2025#59120-competidores-nuevos-newcomers).\n\n* Mximo **4** acompaantes por persona.\n* El precio de la entrada para los alumnos del Colegio Ftima es de $100 pesos uruguayos (deben indicar en los comentarios si este es el caso).\n* El precio de la entrada comn es de $300 pesos uruguayos.\n* No se reembolsar el dinero de la inscripcin bajo ningn concepto. En caso de haber realizado la transferencia, el pago quedar a favor del competidor para su inscripcin en una futura competencia, **solo si nos avisa con una semana de anticipacin o si el evento se cancela.**\n* Ante cualquier duda relacionada al pago de la inscripcin, contacte a la Asociacin Uruguaya de Speedcubing a travs de su pgina de Instagram [@aus.uy](https://www.instagram.com/aus.uy/) o por correo a aus-competitions@googlegroups.com.\n* **Ni los delegados de la WCA ni la organizacin del evento se harn responsables por transferencias que se realicen a cuentas equivocadas.**\n\n#### Pasos para inscribirse:\n1. Completar el registro siguiendo los pasos del tem \"Registro\" (Register).\n2. Si hay lugares libres, recibir un email\\* (puede demorar hasta 24 horas en llegar) con la informacin para pagar.\n3. Realice la transferencia.\n4. Responda al email que contiene la informacin para pagar (con la opcin \"responder a todos\") detallando **nombre/s** y **apellido/s** del competidor y adjuntando una copia del **comprobante** (en su versin electrnica o una foto del ticket), **sin esta informacin, el registro NO ser aceptado**.\n\n\\* El email lo recibir por parte de barrientoslucas7@gmail.com. Se sugiere revisar la direccin del email antes de realizar el pago.\n\n**Notas:**\n* Si no quedan lugares libres, recomendamos a las personas con un registro pendiente que permanezcan alertas en caso de que se libere alguno.\n* En el caso de que no se alcance el lmite de competidores, se aceptarn las inscripciones in situ por orden de llegada.\n\n### **Al proceder con el registro, usted afirma haber ledo y estar de acuerdo con la informacin presente en todos los apartados de este sitio web.**\n\n***\n# ![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBaHBIIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--bacb00caed7d0c9177dc3ea7d687667b270ce30d/6i.png) English \n\n## **READ:**\n\n**NEW COMPETITORS**: You must read [Important](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/70AnosFatimaMontevideo2025#59119-importante-read) and [New competitors](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/70AnosFatimaMontevideo2025#59120-competidores-nuevos-newcomers).\n\n* Maximum **4** guests per competitor.\n* The entrance fee for students of Colegio Ftima is $100 (Uruguayan Pesos). Please indicate in the comments if this is your case.\n* The regular entrance fee is $300 (Uruguayan Pesos).\n* The registration fee will not be refunded under any circumstances. If you have already made the bank transfer, the payment will remain in your favor for a future competition registration. In case you are unable to attend the competition, **you must notify us at least one week before the competition** in order to keep the payment for a future competition.\n* If you have any question, please contact the Asociacin Uruguaya de Speedcubing on Instagram [@aus.uy](https://www.instagram.com/aus.uy/) or by email to aus-competitions@googlegroups.com.\n* **Neither the WCA Delegates nor the organization team will be held responsible for transfers made to wrong bank accounts.**\n\n#### Registration procedure:\n1. Complete your registration by following the steps in the \"Register\" section.\n2. If there are spots available, you will receive an email\\* with the payment information (it may take up to 24 hours to arrive).\n3. Make the transfer.\n4. Reply-all to the email you received with the payment information, detailing **first name/s** and **last name/s** of the competitor and attaching a copy of the **bank transfer receipt** (in its electronic version or a photo of it), **without this information, the registration will NOT be accepted**. Once the transfer has been made, no refunds will be made under any circumstances, except for what has been said above.\n\n\\* You will receive the email from barrientoslucas7@gmail.com. You should check the email address before making the bank transfer.\n\n**Notes:**\n* If registration is full, we recommend people with a pending registration to remain alert in case a spot becomes available.\n* In the case of the competitor limit not being reached, on-the-spot registrations will be accepted in order of arrival at the venue.\n\n### By proceeding with the registration, you confirm that you have read and agree to the statements in all the sections of this website.',0,NULL,NULL,1,2,1,0,4,'![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsiZGF0YSI6ODk2OTMsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--5357a7036160cf087c1c56ee2439e3c02a5826d2/Dise%C3%B1o%20sin%20t%C3%ADtulo%20(1).png)\n# ![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBaGxIIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--e1a87d9563999f890af638f98836b63b2aac90c5/6u.png) Espaol\n\nLmite de competidores: 40.\n\n* El precio de la entrada es de $300 pesos uruguayos.\n* Esta competencia est abierta a competidores de cualquier nacionalidad, cualquier edad y a nuevos competidores, sin importar sus tiempos de resolucin.\n* **COMPETIDORES NUEVOS**: deben leer [Importante](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/70AnosFatimaMontevideo2025#59119-importante-read) y [Competidores nuevos](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/70AnosFatimaMontevideo2025#59120-competidores-nuevos-newcomers).\n* Los competidores deben llevar sus propios puzzles (ver [Directriz 3a+++](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/translations/spanish-american/guidelines.html#3a+++)).\n* Los competidores deben estar presentes y listos para competir cuando se los llama (ver cronograma).\n* Es importante leer toda la informacin disponible en la pgina de la competencia.\n\nAnte cualquier duda, consultar a los organizadores o a los delegados de la WCA.\n\n# ![](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/redirect/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBaHBIIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--bacb00caed7d0c9177dc3ea7d687667b270ce30d/6i.png) English\n\nCompetitor limit: 40.\n\n* The entrance fee is $300 (Uruguayan Pesos).\n* Competitors are responsible for providing their puzzles for the competition (see [Guideline 3a+++](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/regulations/full/#3a+++)).\n* **NEW COMPETITORS**: You must read [Important](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/70AnosFatimaMontevideo2025#59119-importante-read) and [New competitors](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/70AnosFatimaMontevideo2025#59120-competidores-nuevos-newcomers).\n* Competitors must bring their own puzzles.\n* Competitors must be present and ready to compete when called (see the schedule).\n* It is important to read all the information available in the competition\'s website.\n\nFeel free to contact the organizers or the WCA Delegates.',-34904381,-56157776,'333','70 Aos Ftima Montevideo 2025','Ftima is the name of the venue (a school), which turns 70 years old this year (70 aos).',NULL,30000,1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,0,'2025-05-29 02:59:00','2025-05-03 18:30:00','2025-05-02 19:00:18','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2025-06-02 03:33:12',325394,'2025-06-01 21:15:54',1,'2025-05-31','2025-06-02 03:33:12',1,1,'[Colegio Ftima](https://www.colegioyliceofatima.edu.uy/)','General Jos Esteban Brito del Pino 1344, 11300 Montevideo, Uruguay','Entrada por Silvestre Blanco','2025-05-31 20:00:00'),
