('8WingLimited2019',0,0,'2019-02-23 23:07:11',8306,NULL,0,NULL,1500,NULL,NULL,'8 Wing Limited 2019','Astra, Ontario',NULL,0,60,1,'Space and time limitations','2019-02-23 21:25:32',NULL,'','Canada','2019-02-20 03:36:20','CAD',0,'',0,'2019-04-06',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,'After the competitors list reaches 60 competitors, competitors will be added to the waiting list if they register AND pay the registration fee. If anyone on the competitors list deletes their registration, the person at the top of the waiting list will be moved to the competitors list. After the registration period closes, the competitors list will close and everyone who is still on the waiting list will be refunded 100% of their registration fee.\r\n\r\n\r\n',0,NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,NULL,'See tabs for more information.',44107721,-77532784,'333','8 Wing Limited 2019','8 Wing is the name of the military base the venue is located on.',NULL,2000,1,NULL,0,'','2019-03-23 23:00:00',100,'2019-03-30 23:00:00','2019-02-27 14:00:00',NULL,'remarks to the board here',NULL,'2019-04-08 04:47:15',6387,'2019-04-08 02:08:00',1,'2019-04-06','2019-11-01 13:53:04',0,1,'Astra Lounge at 8 Wing Air Force Base','106 Yukon St, Astra, ON, K0K 3W0','The entrance is on Yukon Street. Signs will be posted.',NULL),
('AAAbresiens2025',1,0,'2025-09-06 05:23:01',52559,NULL,0,NULL,500,NULL,NULL,'AAAbrsiens 2025','Les Abrets en Dauphin',NULL,1,80,1,'Size of the venue','2025-09-02 08:15:01',NULL,'','France','2025-07-23 15:23:05','EUR',1,'WCAT: MBLD',1,'2025-11-16','2025-11-13 00:00:00',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'###**[FRANAIS]**\n\nSi vous tes [**adhrente AFS**](https://www.speedcubingfrance.org/association/adhesion) ou que c\'est votre **premire comptition**, l\'inscription est **gratuite**, vous n\'avez donc pas  payer en ligne (mme si la page de paiement s\'affiche). Attendez tout simplement qu\'on accepte votre inscription.\nPlus d\'informations [ici](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/AAAbresiens2025#62737-foire-aux-questions-frequently-asked-questions).\n\nN\'hsitez pas  faire un don lors de votre inscription pour soutenir l\'AFS afin de permettre  cette dernire d\'acheter et de renouveler le matriel franais.\n\n---\n###**[ENGLISH]**\n\nIf you\'re an [**AFS member**](https://www.speedcubingfrance.org/association/adhesion) or if it\'s your **first competition**, the competition is **free**, you don\'t need to pay online (even if the payment page shows up). Just wait for us to accept your registration.\nFor more information, please click [here](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/AAAbresiens2025#62737-foire-aux-questions-frequently-asked-questions).\n\nDo not hesitate to make a donation in order to support the AFS and allow it to buy and renew the French equipment.',0,NULL,NULL,1,1,0,0,NULL,'Linscription est **gratuite** pour les **nouveaux comptiteurs** ainsi que les [**adhrents AFS**](https://www.speedcubingfrance.org/association/adhesion). Si ce n\'est pas votre cas, l\'inscription cote 5.\nMerci de lire attentivement les **conditions d\'inscription, la [FAQ](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/AAAbresiens2025#62737-foire-aux-questions-frequently-asked-questions) et les [tutoriels AFS](https://www.speedcubingfrance.org/speedcubing/tutos)**. \nPensez galement  consulter l\'onglet [Planning](#competition-schedule). \n\n----\nRegistration is **free** for **new competitors** as well as [**AFS members**](https://www.speedcubingfrance.org/association/adhesion), no matter your citizenship or place of residence. Otherwise registration costs 5.\nPlease read the **registration conditions, the [FAQ](https://www.worldcubeassociation.org/competitions/AAAbresiens2025#62737-foire-aux-questions-frequently-asked-questions) and the [AFS tutorials](https://www.speedcubingfrance.org/speedcubing/tutos) carefully**.\nMake sure to read the [Schedule](#competition-schedule) tab. ',45546209,5570745,'clock','Algorithmes Artistiques Abrsiens 2025','Abresiens is the name of the people living in the city of the venue (Les Abrets en Dauphin',NULL,500,0,NULL,0,NULL,'2025-11-10 00:00:00',100,'2025-11-12 23:00:00','2025-09-09 18:00:00','2025-09-08 18:00:24','remarks to the board here',NULL,'2025-11-20 07:04:07',156865,'2025-11-19 20:40:32',1,'2025-11-15','2025-11-20 07:04:07',1,1,'Salle Vercors','185-541 Rte de la Reverdire, 38490 Les Abrets en Dauphin, France','Salle des Fetes de la Ville, entre principale','2025-11-13 00:00:00'),
