(2083,1,'Dear members of our community,\r\n \r\n The WCA Board has appointed Tim Reynolds and Sbastien Auroux as members of the WCA Board.\r\n \r\n Tim Reynolds, from Boston (USA) has been a member of WCA since 2005 and is an active competition organiser and WCA delegate. Tim made important\r\n contributions to WCA as a member of the Results team.\r\n Sbastien Auroux, from Aachen (Germany) has been a member of WCA since 2008 and is an active competition organiser and WCA delegate. Sbastien\r\n contributed to WCA as part of the WCA Regulations Committee and by developing WCA in Germany.\r\n \r\n In the WCA Board Tim will be responsible for the daily operations of the website and the Results team.\r\n Sbastien will be responsible for the WCA Regulations and the follow-up on alleged violations of the regulations.\r\n \r\n WCA Board is also evaluating candidates from Asia for a position in the board.\r\n \r\n We wish Tim and Sbastien good luck in their new positions to represent our community and further develop WCA.\r\n \r\n Cube regards,\r\n \r\n Tyson Mao and Ron van Bruchem\r\n Co-chairmen of WCA\r\n\r\n','2012-07-28 12:27:01',1,'tim-reynolds-and-sebastien-auroux-in-wca-board',0,'Tim Reynolds and Sbastien Auroux in WCA Board',NULL,'2017-06-29 11:42:42'),
